### Suggested order of R scripts for Chapter 1

01_An_introduction_to_R_programming.R
   Covers the elements of R programming including illustration of good practice
01_Evaluating_exp_minus_1.R
   Illustrating how R's expm1(x) evaluates exp(x)-1 in a numerically more stable way
01_Debugging_run_time_and_parallel_computing.R
   Shows how to debug, measure run time and implement parallel computing in R